NTH STREET, N.W., Washington, D.C. 20005<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoHeader style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Trebuchet MS','sans-serif'\">&nbsp; \nTel:&nbsp; (202) 467-5410 </SPAN><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'\">&#8226;</SPAN><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Trebuchet MS','sans-serif'\"> Fax:&nbsp; \n(202) 467-5415<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">To:</SPAN></B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nMembers and Participants</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">From:</SPAN></B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nMichael O'Neil</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">Date:</SPAN></B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nJanuary 14, 2008</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">Subject:</SPAN></B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \n2008 Trilateral Commission Plenary Meeting</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nAttached please find an initial draft of the program for the 2008 Trilateral \nCommission plenary meeting, which will be held in Washington, D.C. April 25-28, \n2008.&nbsp; The meeting will be held at the Ritz Carlton Hotel, 2200 M Street, \nN.W., Washington, D.C. 20037.&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Also \nattached is a room reservation form.&nbsp; Please return the&nbsp;completed form \nby <B>March 14, 2008</B>.&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;An \nupdated version of the program and related materials will be forwarded to you as \nadditional speakers are confirmed.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs